                <h4>Kindergarten & Elementary Education - Subject Areas (21 credits)</h4>

    
              <p>21 credits selected in consultation with the Program Adviser as follows:</p>
<p>12 credits in "teachable" subject area courses of the elementary school curriculum from the lists below for Art, English, Ethics and Religious Culture, French, Mathematics, Music, Natural Sciences, Physical Education, and Social Studies.</p>
<p>And</p>
<p>9 credits, 3 credits from each of any three subject areas not chosen above.</p>
<p>No more than 12 credits may be selected from any single course list.</p>
    
      
      
