  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Religious Studies              : An examination of the moral and spiritual challenges of the modern and post-modern world. Emphasis will also be placed on the role and responsibility of education in meeting these challenges.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              This course is not scheduled for the 2014-2015 academic year.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:              There are no professors associated with this course for the 2014-2015 academic year.          </p>

    
