  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Atmospheric &amp; Oceanic Sciences              : Physical processes associated with severe and hazardous weather affecting the Earth. Topics are taught at a fundamental level, without equations, to provide a complete and up-to-date understanding of such extreme events as blizzards, ice storms, tornadoes, hurricanes, floods and droughts.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Winter 2015          </p>

