                <h4>Physical Education</h4>

    
              <p>Students may take up to 12 credits of Physical Education (EDKP) courses from the list with the permission of the Department of Kinesiology and Physical Education.</p>
<p>* Note: <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/edkp-292">EDKP 292</a> is available as an academic Physical Education course. All other EDKP courses are restricted.</p>
    
              <ul class="program-set">
                  <li class="program-course">
            <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/edkp-204" class="program-course-title">
              EDKP 204 Health Education (3 credits)              <!---->            </a>
