      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Kinesiology&amp;Physical Education              : A study of the teacher's role in the total school health program at both elementary and high school levels; current issues in contemporary health education.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
      Instructors:                        Paula Louise Bush (Fall)                  </p>

    
      </div>

